          "name": "Nervios Tunnels"
        }
      ],
      "description": "A group that hates the \"ever-watching eyes\" and wishes to bring Nervios freedom through contact with the outside world and the destruction of the eyes\r\n\r\n- Quiet / Gaining traction, trying to help people escape, close ties to smugglers.\r\n    \r\n- Truly believes they’re doing what’s best for everyone, especially the people in the town\r\n    \r\n- End goal for the rebels (assuming they know or at least believe all the towers are widely unmanned): expose the truth of the matter. Maybe they want to expose the nobles too. Most likely anti-noble if they know their history (which at least the important ones probably do)\r\n    \r\n- Probably have spies in the guards\r\n    \r\n\r\n- Definitely trying to find some high ups willing to help to learn more about the panopticon\r\n    \r\n\r\n- Often work under darkness or / and with obscuring / illusion spells\r\n    \r\n- Definitely have a tunnel system\r\n    \r\n- Strong aura of secrecy, especially in their upper ranks\r\n    \r\n- Most often help people escape the town\r\n    \r\n- Maybe offers places of solace where the eye cannot see?\r\n    \r\n- The collectivist to the guard / government’s isolationist",
